query:
INSERT INTO eve_credential (
                    character_id,
                    domain,
                    refresh_token,
                    character_main,
                    scopes
                ) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5)
                ON CONFLICT (character_id, domain) DO UPDATE
                SET
                    refresh_token = EXCLUDED.refresh_token,
                    scopes        = EXCLUDED.scopes
